00:31:37.370 --> 00:31:40.460
Quite honestly, I think
the first thing is

00:31:40.460 --> 00:31:47.627
that you have to have-- the
dynamic on my website is,

00:31:47.627 --> 00:31:49.960
basically, there's someone
there to lead the discussion.

00:31:49.960 --> 00:31:51.335
And that would be
me, saying here

00:31:51.335 --> 00:31:52.690
is the topic under discussion.

00:31:52.690 --> 00:31:54.740
Here are my thoughts on
this particular topic

00:31:54.740 --> 00:31:55.770
under discussion.

00:31:55.770 --> 00:31:57.410
The common thread is open.

00:31:57.410 --> 00:31:58.850
Make your comments.

00:31:58.850 --> 00:32:00.580
People come in to
make the comments.

00:32:00.580 --> 00:32:03.670
The person who is refereeing
the conversation-- who

00:32:03.670 --> 00:32:06.982
